data.clean_description: Alprazolam 3 mg per tablet. These are pressed but look great and have some kick to them. XA NAX on one side with the 2 on the other. 4000 delivered via first class. The filler in these makes them just alittle harder than original , but everyone I have dealt with on these love them. They are just alittle larger than the original Pfizer. Give them a try and I m sure you ll be more than happy with them. Thanks.
